# Implementation Guide

The project has an **IMPLEMENTATION.md** at the repo root.

- Before creating or editing summit content, read **IMPLEMENTATION.md**.
- It defines: navigation, file structure, minimum pages (summit.md, agenda.md), and headlines for each page type.
- Use it as the foundation for content changes and new summits.
